[Guest 1]: it would have been a big misstep to turn it into a Bollywood, Bollywoodized, as you put

02:27:19.520 --> 02:27:24.000
[Guest 1]: it spoon feeding sort of ending that that would have been a that wouldn't have worked

02:27:24.000 --> 02:27:28.120
[Guest 1]: for me at all for this film, for this particular film.

