[Guest 1]: The thing is, I don't actually sort of remember the experience of Masaan very clearly right

02:27:43.320 --> 02:27:48.320
[Guest 1]: now to really but but yeah, I think I think definitely not the hyper Bollywoodized version

02:27:48.320 --> 02:27:51.400
[Guest 1]: that that that would definitely not have worked for that film.

02:27:51.400 --> 02:27:54.560
[Guest 1]: What I was saying was, there are different ways of being a participant also right now,

02:27:54.560 --> 02:28:03.280
[Guest 1]: you know, when I get your point about spoon feeding, or about, you know, an insistent

02:28:03.280 --> 02:28:09.040
[Guest 1]: music score underlining things seeming to play your emotions seeming to sort of tell

02:28:09.040 --> 02:28:13.680
[Guest 1]: you what what to feel, but, and again, I suppose this maybe this is different for different

02:28:13.680 --> 02:28:17.600
[Guest 1]: types of viewers, you know, it works differently.

