[Guest 1]: And this Millennium, we're not talking about at all, because we need to get to Amit's list.

04:34:35.120 --> 04:34:41.120
[Amit Varma]: You know, what I'm thinking is that, you know, aur koi sune na sune is episode ko Rajiv Rai sunega.

04:34:41.120 --> 04:34:45.120
[Guest 2]: I mean, more than Rajiv Rai, I hope Sonam listens to it.

