[Unknown]: Sonam is his wife.

04:34:46.120 --> 04:34:48.120
[Unknown]: I'm a big fan.

04:34:48.120 --> 04:34:52.120
[Amit Varma]: Yeah, and yeah, she might send you fan mail, email.

04:34:52.120 --> 04:34:54.120
[Amit Varma]: Not Sonam Kapoor, but Sonam.

04:34:54.120 --> 04:34:57.120
[Unknown]: All three of us are old enough to get that.

